# deploy_conf does not use a repo-root .env for Docker Compose.
# Set CONTAINER_TAG, POSTGRES_*, DB_*, RABBITMQ_*, CHECK_DATABASES_USE_COMPOSE, etc. in Infisical
# (injected by `infisical run` when using Makefile / run.ps1).
# Same for `make down`, `make logs`, `make pull` if variables are not exported: e.g.
#   infisical run --env=dev -- make down
#
# Optional: scripts/regenerate_env_passwords.py can still edit a local file; keep it gitignored if you use one.
